          Revision history
        
         v1.0 BETA on 3/9/1994:
        The first released beta version.
        
         v1.1 BETA on 9/13/1994:
        Added  checking of the screen size. The program now stops for modes
        with  a screen width <> 80. All screen writing now handled directly
        via BIOS calls.
        
         v1.15 on 1/28/1995:
